{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/logo.png?t=1727745960\" /><br><br><strong>Tropicalia: a Brazilian Game</strong> is a RPG set in Brazil before colonization.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/map.gif?t=1727745960\" /><br><br>The game is an ode to SNES-era jRPGs. <br>To spice things up a bit, you will encounter here:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Quick-Time Events</strong> in battle;<br></li><li><strong>Map Skills</strong> for exploration;</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1375760/extras/batt.gif?t=1727745960\" /><br><br>You play as Kaique, a little Guarani warrior, who had his girlfriend kidnapped by the demigod Tau. The plot is based on actual Guarani mythology.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tropicalia is gameplay focused, the dialogue is used to set the atmosphere.</h2><br><br>Gather materials to craft new items. Have fun grinding at quick battles. Test your strategies against challenging bosses.<br><br>Fish, swim, dive, jump, embroil.<br><br>Here you will not meet Dragons and Dwarves. But get ready to face Kurupiras and Boetatas.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Are You Ready For This Tropical Adventure?</h2>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Steps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1375760/876d1f4da310f42ca00e94e383cc79df00e50eb8.jpg"},{"name":"Hardcore","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1375760/876d1f4da310f42ca00e94e383cc79df00e50eb8.jpg"},{"name":"Good ol' Brawl","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1375760/876d1f4da310f42ca00e94e383cc79df00e50eb8.jpg"},{"name":"Black Market","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1375760/876d1f4da310f42ca00e94e383cc79